{"id": "323025", "revid": "513563", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=323025", "title": "WoW Lazy Macros", "text": "&lt;a href=\"http%3A//wowlazymacros.com\"&gt;WoW Lazy Macros&lt;/a&gt; is a blog site dedicated to lazy macros and normal macros in World of Warcraft. It provides continuous updates to their macros for every current patch. Their macro list contains all specs for all classes related to damage (tank,dps).\nThe author of this site also created a plugin addOn for MacroBank add-on called \"&lt;a href=\"http%3A//wow.curse.com/downloads/wow-addons/details/wowlazymacros-plugin-macrobank.aspx\"&gt;WoWLazyMacros Plugin for MacroBank&lt;/a&gt;\" that imports all the lazy macros provided in the site to the game. He also created a community site for the upcoming pet battle system named WoW Pet Battles."}
