{"id": "541364", "revid": "38791128", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=541364", "title": "Patch 7.3.2", "text": "Patch 7.3.2 is a minor patch to \"\", focused around updating a few of the backend systems in addition to making some final adjustments in preparation for the release of the &lt;a href=\"Antorus%2C%20the%20Burning%20Throne\"&gt;Antorus, the Burning Throne&lt;/a&gt; raid.\nThe patch was deployed on the &lt;a href=\"Public%20Test%20Realm\"&gt;Public Test Realm&lt;/a&gt; on September 20, 2017 and released on October 24, 2017.\n\"Last patch notes update: 2017-10-20\"\nUpdates.\nPatch 7.3.2 includes:\nWhile this minor patch adds in additional tuning for Antorus, this raid won\u2019t be available with the release of patch 7.3.2, and will open at a later date."}
